activities.title: Hikes
activities.text: We go hiking around college park and the appalachian trail at least once a month.

activities.title: Socials
activities.text: Member organizations come together bi-annualy for a club social. Come meet new people and make some connections!

activities.title: Volunteering
activities.text: We do a wide range of community service in the College Park area. Some examples are watershed cleanups, invasive species removal, and working soup kitchens.

membership.title: Exit
membership.text: Please proceed to the nearest exit portal
